msgid "We speak about Free Software"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <activityset><activity><description>
#: fsfe.org/activities/whyfs/activity.en.xml:8
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"      Free Software is often referred to as \"Open Source\". But we are\n"
"      convinced that Free Software is the better term: easier to\n"
"      understand, harder to abuse, well-defined, providing additional\n"
"      value, and offering freedom. We connected companies,\n"
"      organisations and even co-founders of the Open Source movement\n"
"      that prefer to use the term Free Software.\n"
"    "
